    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the period in Egypt from about 2325 to 2150 BCE. The period is characterized by internal problems in the royal family and the decentralization of power seen in the general decline of the arts and an increase in provincial tomb building.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000040221/Trigger et al., Ancient Egypt (1983)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Se refiere al período en Egipto desde aproximadamente el 2325 al 2150 a.C. El período se caracteriza por problemas interiores en la familia real y la descentralización del poder vistas en el declive general de las artes y un aumento de la construcción de tumbas en provincias.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Verwijst naar de periode in Egypte van circa 2325 tot 2150 v. Chr. De periode kenmerkt zich door interne problemen in de koninklijke familie en de decentralisatie van de macht, wat tot uitdrukking komt in het algemene verval in de kunsten en een toename van grafbouw in de provincie.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指自西元前2325年至西元前2150年間於埃及發展的時代。此時期特色為王室家庭的內部問題，以及中央集權的崩解，此現象可見於各藝術的普遍衰退以及地方墓室建築的增加。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
